        "created_at": "2018-01-21T21:10:41.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Interesting! So atypically red-fruited in profile?</p>\n<p>Always remember the thrill I felt driving down Olivet Lane for the first time and realizing it was \u2018that\u2019 Olivet Lane.</p>",
